title: Photos: Cole Hamels visits clubhouse, Banister and Daniels reflect as Rangers wrap up season
text: Texas Rangers pitcher Cole Hamels (left) talks to the media as he and teammates clean out their lockers Thursday, October 15, 2015 at Globe Life Ballpark in Arlington, Texas. The Rangers were eliminated from the playoffs following a 6-3 loss to the Toronto Blue Jays Wednesday. (G.J. McCarthy/The Dallas Morning News)
